    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    
    <div class="last-updated">
        <strong>Last Updated:</strong> December 2024
    </div>

    <p>This privacy policy applies to the <span class="app-name">Ferdi</span> app (hereby referred to as "Application") for mobile devices that was created by Pro Imagery (hereby referred to as "Service Provider") as a Free service. This service is intended for use "AS IS".</p>

    <h2>Information Collection and Use</h2>
    <p>The Application collects information when you download and use it. This information may include:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Your email address (for account creation and authentication)</li>
        <li>Your name and username</li>
        <li>Profile photo (if you choose to upload one)</li>
        <li>Travel information you provide (trips, destinations, travel photos)</li>
        <li>Location information you enter (home location, places visited)</li>
        <li>Device information (device type, operating system)</li>
        <li>Usage data (pages visited, time spent in the app)</li>
    </ul>

    <p>The Application does not gather precise real-time location information about your mobile device without your explicit consent.</p>

    <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <p>The Service Provider may use the information you provide to:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Provide and maintain the Application's functionality</li>
        <li>Allow you to connect with other travelers (Travel Buddies feature)</li>
        <li>Display your public profile to other users</li>
        <li>Send important notices and updates about the Application</li>
        <li>Improve and personalize your experience</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p>The Application uses third-party services that may collect information. Below are the links to the privacy policies of third-party service providers used by the Application:</p>
    <ul>
        <li><a href="https://supabase.com/privacy" target="_blank">Supabase</a> (Database and Authentication)</li>
        <li><a href="https://expo.dev/privacy" target="_blank">Expo</a> (App Development Platform)</li>
        <li><a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank">Google Play Services</a></li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Data Storage and Security</h2>
    <p>Your data is stored securely using Supabase, which provides enterprise-grade security including:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Encrypted data transmission (SSL/TLS)</li>
        <li>Encrypted data storage</li>
        <li>Row Level Security for database access</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Data Sharing</h2>
    <p>The Service Provider may share your information in the following situations:</p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>With Other Users:</strong> Your public profile information (name, username, avatar, travel stats) is visible to other users of the Application</li>
        <li><strong>As Required by Law:</strong> To comply with legal obligations or respond to lawful requests</li>
        <li><strong>To Protect Rights:</strong> When we believe disclosure is necessary to protect our rights or safety</li>
    </ul>

    <p>We do not sell your personal information to third parties.</p>

    <h2>User Rights</h2>
    <p>You have the right to:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Access your personal data</li>
        <li>Correct inaccurate information</li>
        <li>Delete your account and associated data</li>
        <li>Block other users from viewing your profile</li>
        <li>Report inappropriate content</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Data Retention</h2>
    <p>The Service Provider will retain your data for as long as you use the Application and for a reasonable time thereafter. If you wish to delete your data, you can delete your account through the Application settings or contact us directly.</p>

    <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
    <p>The Application does not address anyone under the age of 13. The Service Provider does not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If you are a parent or guardian and believe your child has provided personal information, please contact us so we can remove that information.</p>

    <h2>Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
    <p>The Service Provider may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page and updating the "Last Updated" date.</p>

    <div class="contact-box">
        <h2 style="margin-top: 0; border: none; padding-top: 0;">Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or our data practices, please contact us at:</p>
        <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:privacy@proimagery.com">privacy@proimagery.com</a></p>
    </div>

